  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare between the addition of Mg sulphate or Nalbuphine to
      intraperitoneal bupivacaine installation in laparoscopic hysterectomy for postoperative pain
      control and their relative adverse effects.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
